  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of APART is the assessment of the therapeutic and preventive stimulation algorithms
      of the Medtronic AT500 and following devices in patients with atrial tachyarrhythmias and an
      indication for cardiac pacing according to the German guidelines. Medication is controlled
      throughout the study with a beta-blocker as the only antiarrhythmic drug.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
