  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Indication for cardiac pacing according to the German guidelines

          -  Documented (electrocardiogram; ECG) atrial arrhythmia during the last three months
             before enrollment

          -  Willingness to terminate antiarrhythmic drugs until the first recurrence of an atrial
             arrhythmia

          -  Sinus rhythm during 24 hours before implant of the device

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Ejection fraction below 40%

          -  Mechanic prosthesis of the tricuspid valve

          -  Indication to implantable cardioverter defibrillator (ICD)-implantation

          -  Pregnancy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
